Life is always easier with friends. But what if one of them goes missing? Grab your weapon and jump, shoot and dodge in this action-packed side-scroller adventure. Fight your way through enemies to find your lost friend in this twisted world!

Your friend went missing, and a dark force is looming in this already deranged world. You, Sheriff Toadster, are the only toad that can save him in this intense action-packed side-scroller adventure! Jump around, shoot your way through and investigate the mysterious disappearance, all while exploring the land and meeting the intriguing characters of this universe!

author: PlayStation
description:
https://www.playstation.com/games/atomfall

Surrounded by murky and perilous waters lies a wicked isle… a mysterious new region to explore, nestled off the Cumberland coast. They say there was a creepy old fishing village out there, but the locals haven’t seen anyone from there for years. 

There is a boat from the Wyndham Village shore for anyone brave enough to go and look for themselves. New mysteries, new supplies and new possibilities of escape could lie ahead for anyone who dares.

The Atomfall story continues with Story Expansion Pack: Wicked Isle, coming to Playstation 5 and Playstation 4 on June 3rd 2025.

A single-player survival-action game inspired by real-life events, Atomfall is set five years after the Windscale nuclear disaster in Northern England. 

Explore the fictional quarantine zone, scavenge, craft, barter, fight and talk your way through a British countryside setting filled with bizarre characters, mysticism, cults, and rogue government agencies. 
From Rebellion
title: Atomfall - Story Expansion Trailer | PS5 & PS4 Games

Mongooses in a box! Nikoderiko: The Magical World - Director’s Cut is getting a physical retail edition and a deluxe Collector's Edition, coming to PlayStation®5 on August 22, 2025. 

The standard edition contains a physical copy of the game on PS5®, while the Collector's Edition features the game, the Original Soundtrack by genre legend David Wise and an exclusive artbook. Discover more at nikoderiko-game.com and pre-order your copy online or at your local retailer today!

Adventure with Niko and Luna in this platforming gem for all ages! Chill out with Easy Mode, put your skills to the test with with Hard Mode, and partner up with a friend for exciting couch co-op. The free Director's Cut update lets you earn extra Trophies, explore brand-new levels, enjoy polished and optimized gameplay, and hear Niko and friends speak in eight fully dubbed languages.

#ps5 #ps5games #nikoderiko
title: Nikoderiko: The Magical World - Box Announcement Trailer | PS5 Games
